	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Toki_(video_game)" class="postlink">Toki</a> had nearly arcade perfect ports to Amiga and Atari ST.<br /><br />The NES port of Toki was very tastefully (IMO) adapted to the limitations of the NES while retaining a very similar feel and flavour to the original.<br /><br />The Genesis port of Toki (subtitled &quot;Going Ape Spit&quot;, ugh) had a complete level redesign.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


