		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Sumez wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I always though Going Ape Spit was a sequel?</div><br />It's not. It has the same story, and more or less the same level progression and bosses, mostly the same music.<br /><br />Aside from the levels there's a bunch of arbitrary changes, like no G'n'G style map between levels, characters renamed, etc. It's really bizarre to me... the only explanation I could think of is that they had a mandate to make the game longer, which meant making new levels anyway? (Personally I found the Ape Spit levels pretty boring by comparison.)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
